data.description: An adorable bungalow with 4 bedrooms and 1 car attached garage just waiting for a new owner. Enter your home to the living room open to the dining room and kitchen. High vaulted ceilings with recessed lighting. You have 2 bedrooms and a full bath upstairs. Downstairs is 2 more nicely sized bedrooms and a recreation area with a wet bar perfect for large gatherings and another full bath. Outdoors is a covered patio area with fenced in backyard. With a little TLC this could be a great starter home or investment property to add to your portfolio. Call today to schedule your personal tour today.
